          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Mitigating Attacks on Diplomats Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to study the means of countering hypersonic acoustic attacks on Foreign Service officers and their families, including methods to support the physical protection of U.S. embassies, consulates, and embassy residences. </p>]]></text>
